    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_2463684513" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2463684513" />
    <a title="Beata" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/47571190-beata"><img alt="Beata" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1505761623p2/47571190.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2463684513?book_show_action=true">Aug 26, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Beata" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Beata" href="/user/show/47571190-beata">Beata</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2463684513" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6043133460984364531">This is a powefrul book on murders committed on Osage people during the second decade of the 20th century. The author is an investigative journalist and does a tremendous job bringing this tragic story to the general public. I was astounded and could not put this book down... </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

